comment._content: Lockheed 12A Electra Junior NC17374 c/n 1218 Superior Oil Co, photo Robert Yarnall Richie, March 1940, Houston, Texas.  This photo was used in a Lockheed magazine ad.  NC17374 was written off in a crash McKilligan Canyon November 3, 1944.
